The Glenn Beck Program



The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET



        
      
      The Glenn Beck Program 3/31/14Monday, March 31, 2014 



 Glenn shares with the world amazing times during the life of his father, 
              who just recently passed away. 

 Doc Thompson weighs in on the Eric Cantor/GOP/George Soros connection,

 FreedomWorks Vice President Adam Brandon discusses the 2014 midterms
   and Representative Ted Poe joins the program to discuss the movement
     to enhance privacy in America. 

        That and more on The Glenn Beck Program!Media files
